    <p>
        %product% is a JetBrains IDE based on the
        <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/opensource/idea/">IntelliJ platform</a>.
        Use it to author, build, test, and publish technical documentation.</p>
    <note>
        If you want to use %product% as a plugin for another JetBrains IDE,
        see.
    </note>
    <procedure title="Install %product%">
        <step>
            <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/writerside/download">Download</a> the %product% installer.
        </step>
        <step>
            Run the installer.
        </step>
    </procedure>

    <p>
        %product% is a plugin for <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/idea/">IntelliJ IDEA</a>
        and other JetBrains IDEs based on the IntelliJ platform.
        Use it to author, build, test, and publish technical documentation.</p>
    <note>
        If you want to use %product% as a standalone product,
        see.
    </note>
    <procedure id="install" title="Install %product%">
        <step>
            If you do not have a JetBrains IDE,
            <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/idea/download/#section=mac">download</a>
            and install IntelliJ IDEA
            (the free Community Edition is enough).
        </step>
        <step>
            Open the IDE settings and select
            <control>Plugins</control>
            .
        </step>
        <step>
            Switch to the
            <control>Marketplace</control>
            tab,
            search for <code>Writerside</code>,
            select the plugin, and click
            <control>Install</control>
            .

        </step>
    </procedure>

    Watch this short video for an overview of the %product% UI and main features:

    <video src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wjGPVFF1oHw" width="704"/>

